English: Subject will get less out of MediPacks.
Description:
Don't localize MediPacks. 
Describes the disadvantage of having a poor "med efficiency" value. Essentially this means that when the subject uses a MediPack, it will replenish less health than usual.

French.Translation: Le sujet tire moins de bénéfices des MediPacks.

Italian.Translation: Il soggetto otterrà benefici minori dai MediPack.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto les sacará menos partido a los botiquines.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo é menos beneficiado pelos pacotes médicos.

Polish.Translation: Biorca odzyska mniej zdrowia po użyciu apteczki.

Japanese.Translation: 対象へのMediPacksの効果が下がる。

Korean.Translation: 대상이 구급팩 효과를 더 적게 받습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象將從醫藥包[MediPack]獲益較少。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 医药包治疗使用者的效果降低。
